
# 🎨 SketchyArts – Full Stack Art Gallery & E-Commerce Web App

SketchyArts is a feature-rich full-stack website where users can browse artworks, purchase custom art, and track orders — built with the MERN stack.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React.js (with React Router DOM)
- **Backend**: Node.js + Express.js
- **Database**: MongoDB Atlas
- **Authentication**: JWT + bcrypt
- **Email**: Nodemailer (with Gmail App Password)
- **Image Hosting**: Cloudinary

