## 📦 Installation & Setup 

## Backend Setup (`/server`)

cd server
npm install
node index.js

Your site is now running on:  
📍 http://localhost:5000 or your server's IP.

## Frontend Setup (`/client`)

cd client
npm install
npm start

Your site is now running on:  
📍 http://localhost:3000 or your server's IP.

