## 🔐 Features

- ✅ User authentication (Signup with OTP, Login)
- 🖼️ Art gallery (upload & view)
- 🛒 Add to Cart and Checkout
- 💳 Payment Instructions (Paytm/GPay/PhonePe)
- 📦 Order Tracking (Ordered → Packed → Shipped → Delivered)
- 📧 Order confirmation and status emails
- 📂 Admin Dashboard:
  - Upload gallery and sale items
  - Manage orders and users
  - Track earnings, update homepage text, coupons
- 📱 Fully responsive (mobile-friendly design)

